  "time_ut": 1657858673,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0b85\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4 7 \u0ba8\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bc1\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baf \u0b9c\u0ba9\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bbf - \u0b9a\u0baa\u0bbe\u0ba8\u0bbe\u0baf\u0b95\u0bb0\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "New President - Speaker in next 7 days",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Speaker Mahinda Yappa Abeywardena said that Prime Minister Ranil Wickremesinghe will act as Acting President until a new President is appointed as per the Constitution.",
        "He said he intends to convene Parliament on Saturday, July 16 to begin parliamentary proceedings to appoint a new president.",
        "In addition, Speaker Mahinda Yappa Abeywardena has also stated that he intends to complete the parliamentary activities to elect a new president within the next 7 days.",
        "\u201cMy intention is to conduct the parliamentary affairs necessary to elect a new president as soon as possible in accordance with the provisions of the Constitution. I request all party leaders to extend their support for this,\u201d he said.",
        "The Speaker has requested all political parties and Parliament to maintain democracy during this period."
      ],
